      "rationale": "Material elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (827 MPa), and tangent modulus (1.2 GPa) sourced from internal coupon testing dataset (dataVintage 2025-11-20). Geometry from CAD drawings at revision D. Sensitivity analysis confirms stiffness QoI varies <4% across the measured property range. Re-validation of material inputs against the updated model revision (2026-02-14) is planned for Q2 2026 but has not yet been completed."
    },
