      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate the physiological loading environment and span the range of clinically relevant conditions.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 configuration (35 mm offset, 10 mm/min crosshead speed, ambient temperature). Only one load condition evaluated; cyclic and combined loading not included. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3); this shortfall is acknowledged and flagged in the decision record. The single static condition is nonetheless representative of the primary regulatory submission requirement."
    },
