      "rationale": "Crosshead displacement rate converted to equivalent quasi-static loading in FEA. Fixture geometry modeled explicitly from metrology data. Material properties assigned per lot-specific coupon test results. Mapping documented in simulation plan SP-COU1-2025 with traceability matrix linking each FEA input to its experimental source."
